# 📋 Drag & Drop Todo App

A modern and responsive **Drag & Drop Todo Application** built using **HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript**.

This application allows users to create tasks, edit them, delete them, drag tasks between different columns, and save everything using **localStorage**.

This project was built as part of my **Frontend Development Journey – Day 24** to strengthen my understanding of CRUD operations, Drag & Drop API, DOM Manipulation, localStorage, and JavaScript Event Handling.

---

# 🚀 Live Demo

🔗 Live Website: https://todolistmarked.netlify.app/

---

