# 🔄 Application Flow

```
Add Task
    │
    ▼
Create Task Object
    │
    ▼
Save into Array
    │
    ▼
Save into localStorage
    │
    ▼
Render Task
    │
    ▼
Drag Task
    │
    ▼
Drop into New Column
    │
    ▼
Update Status
    │
    ▼
Save Again
```

---

# 📦 Task Object

```javascript
{
    id: Date.now(),

    title: "Learn JavaScript",

    status: "todo"
}
```

Possible status values

```
todo
progress
done
```

