# 🆕 New Features Learned

This project introduced several new JavaScript concepts.

## HTML5 Drag & Drop API

Allows users to drag an element from one location and drop it into another.

Events used:

- dragstart
- dragover
- dragleave
- drop
- dragend

---

## draggable Attribute

```html
<div draggable="true">
```

Makes an HTML element draggable.

---

## dataset

Store extra information inside HTML.

Example

```html
<div data-id="101">
```

JavaScript

```javascript
element.dataset.id
```

Output

```
101
```

---

## Dynamic Status Update

When a task moves,

Before

```
status = "todo"
```

After

```
status = "progress"
```

No new object is created.

Only the status changes.

